      "layout": "The page is a full-bleed dark canvas with content largely left-aligned and centrally focused. There is no explicit max-width for the main content block, giving a spacious, open feel. The hero section prominently features a large, interactive 3D graphic. Text is structured in distinct blocks with generous vertical spacing (64px `sectionGap`). Social links are stacked vertically on the right, providing a clear access point. The layout gives ample breathing room, highlighting individual content elements rather than dense information.",
